Name: Final Preparations
Description: There is no one on the shop-floor today. But you can hear the Tobacconist in the workshop above.

DefaultEvent.Description: "We're done gathering flavours, [q:Addressed As]," he shouts as you ascend. "We'll make do with what we have. Let's finish it."

ChildBranches.Name: "Come up!"
ChildBranches.Description: What's the Tobacconist shouting about now?
